OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FReforms to the way Ofsted inspects
OL,7,Fschools, including new report cards
OL,8,Fwith a five-point grading scale, will
OL,9,Fcome into place from November.
OL,11,FParents will be given more detail
OL,12,Fabout their children's education with
OL,13,Fthe introduction of these new-look
OL,14,Freport cards, Ofsted has confirmed.
