OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FSchools in England will be graded
OL,7,Facross a variety of different areas `
OL,8,Fincluding attendance, behaviour and
OL,9,Finclusion, using a colour-coded five-
OL,10,Fpoint scale, which Ofsted says will
OL,11,Fprovide parents with "more granularity
OL,12,Fand nuance about a provider's
OL,13,Fperformance."
OL,15,FFollowing feedback from parents and
OL,16,Feducation professionals, the five
OL,17,Fgrades have been renamed 'urgent
OL,18,Fimprovement', 'needs attention',
OL,19,F'expected standard', 'strong
OL,20,Fstandard', and the new highest grade
OL,21,Fof 'exceptional'.
