OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FAn independent poll by YouGov found
OL,7,Fthat almost seven out of ten parents
OL,8,Fsurveyed preferred the new-look report
OL,9,Fcards to Ofsted's current inspection
OL,10,Freports, with nine out of ten saying
OL,11,Fthey were easy to understand.
OL,13,FIn the early years, Ofsted will
OL,14,Fincrease the frequency of inspections
OL,15,Ffrom every six years to every four,
OL,16,Fwith an enhanced focus on the quality
OL,17,Fof education and care.
