OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FSchools in England used to be issued
OL,7,Fwith one of four judgments for overall
OL,8,Feffectiveness ` outstanding, good,
OL,9,Frequires improvement and inadequate `
OL,10,Fwhen inspected, but this was scrapped
OL,11,Flast year following criticism of the
OL,12,Finspection system since the death of
OL,13,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry.
OL,15,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,16,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,17,FPrimary School in Reading from its
OL,18,Fhighest rating of "outstanding" to its
OL,19,Flowest rating, "inadequate", over
OL,20,Fsafeguarding concerns.
