OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FProfessor Julia Waters, sister of Ruth
OL,7,FPerry, has been highly critical of
OL,8,FOfsted's new plans, branding them a
OL,9,F"cosmetic rebranding, tweaking, and
OL,10,Fexpansion of the same unreliable and
OL,11,Fpunishing system as the one before."
OL,13,FIn a statement released after Ofsted
OL,14,Fannounced a raft of changes of
OL,15,FTuesday, including a new colour-coded
OL,16,Fscale grading a variety of areas
OL,17,Fincluding attendance, behaviour and
OL,18,Finclusion, Prof Waters said the
OL,19,Freforms are an "over-complicated mish-
OL,20,Fmash" and should be halted.
