OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FConcerns have also been raised by the
OL,7,FNational Education Union, which
OL,8,Fclaimed, "Nando's-style" won't keep
OL,9,Fpupils safe or boost good teaching.
OL,11,FHis Majesty's Chief Inspector Sir
OL,12,FMartyn Oliver insisted however:
OL,13,F"Ofsted exists to keep children safe
OL,14,Fand improve their lives.
OL,16,F"Children deserve the best possible
OL,17,Feducation; their parents deserve the
OL,18,Fbest possible information and
OL,19,Feducation professionals deserve to
OL,20,Fhave their work fairly assessed by
OL,21,Fexperts.
