OL,3,CNew Ofsted 'report cards' to be rolled
OL,4,Cout to parents from November
OL,6,FAn independent report by Sinead
OL,7,FMcBrearty, the chief executive of
OL,8,Fcharity Education Support, said that
OL,9,Fstakeholders had called for the roll-
OL,10,Fout of the changes to be stopped or
OL,11,Fslowed down, while Mrs Perry's sister
OL,12,FProfessor Julia Waters has also urged
OL,13,Fthe Education Secretary to halt them.
OL,15,FAddressing these concerns, Sir Martyn
OL,16,Fsaid there would be a "steady and
OL,17,Fassured start" to inspection and added
OL,18,Fthat the reforms have been "called for
OL,19,Ffor a long time".
